  "remarks": "Acts for IRISL in the Middle East. It is a subsidiary of Azores Shipping Company. Its Managing Director is Mohammad Moghaddami Fard. In October 2010 it was involved in setting up cover companies; the names of the new ones to be used on bills of lading in order to circumvent sanctions. It continues to be involved in the scheduling of IRISL ships.",
